from(bucket: "vtb")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "win_services")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "state")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["display_name"] == "MinervaEngineSvc_MinervaEngineV4 - сервис клиентского обслуживания ВТБ24-Онлайн")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["host"] == "ltvolm-ap5001wv")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["service_name"] == "MinervaEngineSvc_MinervaEngineV4")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")
